      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LOTS TO LOVE (2) deep into the campaign and gets the right set-up with Dalton's claim. Closed strongly with the 60kg to finish second over 2100m at Tamworth. Backs-up quickly and finds a winnable race. CALZINO (3) showed potential last prep in tougher company and indicated he was near his best with a tidy fourth over 2100m at Tamworth. Senior rider hops aboard and can figure prominently. MICROGRAVITY (4) winkers go on today and should get the 2000m at his sixth race start. Made good improvement in the first prep and can figure prominently. THINK I'M IN (10) had mixed luck in his three career starts and bred to run the 2000m. Desperate for a firmer surface with the tongue-tie going on. Place preferred.",
